      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">A neurophysiologist is conducting a seminar on membrane potentials, focusing on the equilibrium potential differences across various muscle cells and neurons. She presents a case where different cell types have different resting membrane potentials. What are the equilibrium potentials for neurons, skeletal muscle, and smooth muscle?</span></span></span></span></p>",
