          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">RMP of -90 mV and a firing threshold of -70 mV. </span></span></span></span></p>"
